{"id":"jezreel-portion-of","term":"Jezreel, Portion of","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>The field adjoining the city (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Kings 9:10\">2 Kings 9:10</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Kings 9:21\">21</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Kings 9:36\">36</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Kings 9:37\">37</a>). Here Naboth was stoned to death (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 21:13\">1 Kings 21:13</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["2 Kings 9:10","2 Kings 9:21","2 Kings 9:36","2 Kings 9:37","1 Kings 21:13"]}